ghar (git: home as repository)

INSTALL
=======
 $ cp ghar $SOMEWHERE_IN_THE_PATH
 $ ghar init
 $ ghar create dotfiles			# to create your first ghar repo
 $ ghar dotfiles add .ghar/config	# Add your first config file: ghar's
 $ ghar dotfiles commit -m "Initial .ghar/config"
 $ ghar dotfiles remote add origin user@host:~/dotfiles.git
 $ ghar dotfiles push origin master
